Vietnam May Restrict Deposit Insurance to Local Currency Only

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-19T02:42:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/vietnam-may-restrict-deposit-insurance-to-local-currency-only.html
Vietnam  may restrict deposit
insurance to local currency deposits only, the National Assembly
said in a draft law document released at a briefing in Hanoi
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
